Vanessa: Are you ready, this one's coming in faster!
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu~
Vanessa: Dang, you got me! You little...
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu~
Vanessa: You think that's funny? Time for my special move, the wrecking ball!
Golemwalt: Grrouu!?
Vanessa: Bears!?
Razorclaw: So this is where the golem was taken.
Crushfang: Stealing our golem, human!?
Vanessa: No, no, not at all. The big guy got lost, all I did was...
Crushfang: Nonsense! All you people see are gem rocks! Now it's time to pay the price!
Crushfang: What the...!?
Razorclaw: This golem... is protecting the human?
Crushfang: She got away!
Razorclaw: Let's get her!
Vanessa: No sign of anyone... did we get away?

Vanessa: I-I've never been so close to bears before... 
I thought I was dead meat.
Vanessa: Golemwalt, you attacked those bears just to save my butt? Why?
Golemwalt: Grrrouuu~
Vanessa: Thank you. I-I owe you my life...
